---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Transporting Your Surfboard: Every Method Explained - Surf Deeper" description="Carry, bike, and car transport options for surfboards with safety-first tips and setup outlines.">
  <header class="page-header">
    <h1>Transporting Your Surfboard: Every Method Explained</h1>
    <p class="page-subtitle">Practical setups for foot, bike, and car</p>
  </header>

  <article class="technique-article">
    <section>
      <h2>On Foot</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Underarm carry</li>
        <li>On head</li>
        <li>Resting vertically on foot</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>By Bike</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Side racks vs. trailers</li>
        <li>Balance and safety</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>By Car (Outside)</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Hard racks with cam straps</li>
        <li>Soft racks / temp racks</li>
        <li>Stacking multiple boards (nose/tail alternation, padding)</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>By Car (Inside)</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Fitting shortboards vs. longboards</li>
        <li>Seat-down hacks</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Board Bags & Protection</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Day bags</li>
        <li>Board socks</li>
        <li>Travel coffins (airline travel tips)</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Strapping & Safety</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Nose forward, fins up rule</li>
        <li>Cam straps vs. ratchet straps (pros/cons)</li>
        <li>Avoiding strap vibration</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    color: #00ff88;
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }

  .page-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #00ff88;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .technique-article {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .technique-article section {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .technique-article h2 {
    color: #00ff88;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #00ff88;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .technique-article ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .technique-article li {
    color: #00ff88;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .technique-article li::before {
    content: "â—¦";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #00cc6a;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-header h1 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
    }
    .technique-article {
      padding: 0 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>


